[
  {
    "startTime": 2460,
    "endTime": 4300,
    "duration": 1840,
    "text": "I'm so glad you're joining the Literature Club!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4740,
    "endTime": 6280,
    "duration": 1540,
    "text": "Hey, I never agreed to join..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6660,
    "endTime": 8080,
    "duration": 1420,
    "text": "Oh wow, Sayori! Who's your friend?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8420,
    "endTime": 10120,
    "duration": 1700,
    "text": "He's our club's newest member!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10400,
    "endTime": 12320,
    "duration": 1920,
    "text": "That's...not set in stone..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12860,
    "endTime": 13900,
    "duration": 1040,
    "text": "This is Monika!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14740,
    "endTime": 15580,
    "duration": 840,
    "text": "Yuri!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16460,
    "endTime": 17340,
    "duration": 880,
    "text": "and Natsuki!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17900,
    "endTime": 18960,
    "duration": 1060,
    "text": "...and you already know me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19560,
    "endTime": 20760,
    "duration": 1200,
    "text": "Welcome to our meeting!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21040,
    "endTime": 22140,
    "duration": 1100,
    "text": "Are you into reading?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22280,
    "endTime": 23880,
    "duration": 1600,
    "text": "No need for being coy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24780,
    "endTime": 26060,
    "duration": 1280,
    "text": "We'll improve your uptake!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26140,
    "endTime": 27220,
    "duration": 1080,
    "text": "Have a friggin' cupcake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27440,
    "endTime": 28840,
    "duration": 1400,
    "text": "and must you bring a boy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29820,
    "endTime": 31080,
    "duration": 1260,
    "text": "Time to write some poems!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31140,
    "endTime": 32180,
    "duration": 1040,
    "text": "Don't be scared to show 'em!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32240,
    "endTime": 34600,
    "duration": 2360,
    "text": "The festival's days away!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34600,
    "endTime": 35940,
    "duration": 1340,
    "text": "You could help with baking!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35940,
    "endTime": 37020,
    "duration": 1080,
    "text": "Or with banner making!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37300,
    "endTime": 39540,
    "duration": 2240,
    "text": "And I'll walk home alone today..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40060,
    "endTime": 40940,
    "duration": 880,
    "text": "Maybe we're friends..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41340,
    "endTime": 42240,
    "duration": 900,
    "text": "Maybe we're more..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42240,
    "endTime": 44600,
    "duration": 2360,
    "text": "How could he love a simple girl next door?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44720,
    "endTime": 49700,
    "duration": 4980,
    "text": "I'm just not the type he's looking for!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50180,
    "endTime": 53180,
    "duration": 3000,
    "text": "Hey, Sayori, you doing okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53800,
    "endTime": 55800,
    "duration": 2000,
    "text": "I'm having a difficult day..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55880,
    "endTime": 59720,
    "duration": 3840,
    "text": "I'd say! You seem pretty lonely!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60500,
    "endTime": 62080,
    "duration": 1580,
    "text": "I wish I could make her grin..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62080,
    "endTime": 64520,
    "duration": 2440,
    "text": "...all she wants are things back the way they've been."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64520,
    "endTime": 67060,
    "duration": 2540,
    "text": ".̴̝̪̮͌.̵̗͛.̷̧̛̒ She's depressed and stressed and she's feeling blue..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67060,
    "endTime": 70200,
    "duration": 3140,
    "text": "So I don't want Sayori hanging around you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70720,
    "endTime": 72520,
    "duration": 1800,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73160,
    "endTime": 75120,
    "duration": 1960,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75760,
    "endTime": 77540,
    "duration": 1780,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77920,
    "endTime": 78860,
    "duration": 940,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78860,
    "endTime": 80260,
    "duration": 1400,
    "text": "JUST JUST MONIKA!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80260,
    "endTime": 82420,
    "duration": 2160,
    "text": "I'm so glad you're joining the Literature Club!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82420,
    "endTime": 83460,
    "duration": 1040,
    "text": "Wait! What happened to Sayori"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83460,
    "endTime": 84460,
    "duration": 1000,
    "text": "Wait! What happened to Ｓａｙｏｒｉ"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84580,
    "endTime": 85200,
    "duration": 620,
    "text": "Who?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85220,
    "endTime": 87160,
    "duration": 1940,
    "text": "There's no one here named that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87960,
    "endTime": 89220,
    "duration": 1260,
    "text": "Manga is my passion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89300,
    "endTime": 90460,
    "duration": 1160,
    "text": "Don't you dare be bashin'!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90460,
    "endTime": 92660,
    "duration": 2200,
    "text": "The writing's got finesse!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92940,
    "endTime": 94220,
    "duration": 1280,
    "text": "Maybe you should borrow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94220,
    "endTime": 95600,
    "duration": 1380,
    "text": "these until tomorrow..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95600,
    "endTime": 97180,
    "duration": 1580,
    "text": "Were you looking up my dress?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97900,
    "endTime": 99300,
    "duration": 1400,
    "text": "Let's go read a story!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99300,
    "endTime": 100180,
    "duration": 880,
    "text": "What about Ｓａｙｏｒｉ"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100300,
    "endTime": 102240,
    "duration": 1940,
    "text": "Let's talk about me instead!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102680,
    "endTime": 104240,
    "duration": 1560,
    "text": "I've been learning piano!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104240,
    "endTime": 105360,
    "duration": 1120,
    "text": "And I sing soprano!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105360,
    "endTime": 107700,
    "duration": 2340,
    "text": "And I can't get you out of my head!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107700,
    "endTime": 108980,
    "duration": 1280,
    "text": "Can't look away..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109200,
    "endTime": 110340,
    "duration": 1140,
    "text": "Can't help but blush..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110800,
    "endTime": 112600,
    "duration": 1800,
    "text": "Where did I get this overwhelming crush?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113000,
    "endTime": 117760,
    "duration": 4760,
    "text": "It's sharp as a knife and twice the rush!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118140,
    "endTime": 118640,
    "duration": 500,
    "text": "Yo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119420,
    "endTime": 121540,
    "duration": 2120,
    "text": "There's something I think you should know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121540,
    "endTime": 123000,
    "duration": 1460,
    "text": "I've never seen Yuri so-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123180,
    "endTime": 124860,
    "duration": 1680,
    "text": "sAnE aNd cHiLL"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125260,
    "endTime": 127820,
    "duration": 2560,
    "text": "ANd sTiLL kinda sweaty..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127820,
    "endTime": 130500,
    "duration": 2680,
    "text": "And I don't mind cutting to the chase."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130500,
    "endTime": 132740,
    "duration": 2240,
    "text": "I'm in love with you and your gorgeous face!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132900,
    "endTime": 135140,
    "duration": 2240,
    "text": "That's a sentiment I can't allow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135300,
    "endTime": 138240,
    "duration": 2940,
    "text": "So my dear friend Yuri is getting the point now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138860,
    "endTime": 140740,
    "duration": 1880,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141000,
    "endTime": 143280,
    "duration": 2280,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143620,
    "endTime": 145820,
    "duration": 2200,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA! (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146120,
    "endTime": 147000,
    "duration": 880,
    "text": "JUST MONIKA!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147020,
    "endTime": 148340,
    "duration": 1320,
    "text": "JUST JUST MONIKA!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148800,
    "endTime": 149640,
    "duration": 840,
    "text": ".̴̝̪̮͌.̵̗͛.̷̧̛̒ Could you have guessed?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149640,
    "endTime": 150520,
    "duration": 880,
    "text": "Maybe you knew?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150920,
    "endTime": 153000,
    "duration": 2080,
    "text": "Natsuki is next, I'm deleting .̴̝̪̮͌.̵̗͛.̷̧̛̒  her too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153740,
    "endTime": 156280,
    "duration": 2540,
    "text": "We don't need cupcakes or poems or tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156280,
    "endTime": 157940,
    "duration": 1660,
    "text": "I only need you to love me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158500,
    "endTime": 159300,
    "duration": 800,
    "text": ".̴̝̪̮͌.̵̗͛.̷̧̛̒"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159840,
    "endTime": 164100,
    "duration": 4260,
    "text": "Wow. That's a lot of CrunchyRoll you've been watching. You're really taking advantage of that free VRV trial."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164220,
    "endTime": 164720,
    "duration": 500,
    "text": "Aah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164780,
    "endTime": 167960,
    "duration": 3180,
    "text": "Hey...there's no one else in our way..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168440,
    "endTime": 172260,
    "duration": 3820,
    "text": "So look at me and just say, right here, my dear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172640,
    "endTime": 173980,
    "duration": 1340,
    "text": "that you love me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174520,
    "endTime": 176920,
    "duration": 2400,
    "text": "And we'll sit here till the end of time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176920,
    "endTime": 179320,
    "duration": 2400,
    "text": "cause I've earned this and you're finally mine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179420,
    "endTime": 181740,
    "duration": 2320,
    "text": "And I'm sorry what you've had to see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182020,
    "endTime": 185040,
    "duration": 3020,
    "text": "But it no longer matters, 'cause now you belong to me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185280,
    "endTime": 189760,
    "duration": 4480,
    "text": "Forever. Forever. (x2)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190220,
    "endTime": 192440,
    "duration": 2220,
    "text": "FOREVER. FOREVER."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192560,
    "endTime": 193520,
    "duration": 960,
    "text": "FOREVER."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194260,
    "endTime": 194900,
    "duration": 640,
    "text": "F̴̖́o̴̠͋̕ř̷̛͔ę̷̐v̴̗̟͋è̸̪̋͂ŕ̷̼͋!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196560,
    "endTime": 198560,
    "duration": 2000,
    "text": "Well look what the dragged in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199100,
    "endTime": 199660,
    "duration": 560,
    "text": "Sayori?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200400,
    "endTime": 201600,
    "duration": 1200,
    "text": "You're still in the Literature Club?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202200,
    "endTime": 204020,
    "duration": 1820,
    "text": "Of course! I'm the president, after all!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204800,
    "endTime": 206500,
    "duration": 1700,
    "text": "Wow, Sayori! Who's your friend?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206740,
    "endTime": 207800,
    "duration": 1060,
    "text": "He's our newest member!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208140,
    "endTime": 210180,
    "duration": 2040,
    "text": "I'm guessing that's not set in stone..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211240,
    "endTime": 213140,
    "duration": 1900,
    "text": "This time, I think it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213960,
    "endTime": 215400,
    "duration": 1440,
    "text": "Why don't you join us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215400,
    "endTime": 217780,
    "duration": 2380,
    "text": "I was just getting Natsuki here into my favorite horror novel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217780,
    "endTime": 220380,
    "duration": 2600,
    "text": "Hey! It's...it's not like I like it or anything..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221480,
    "endTime": 223920,
    "duration": 2440,
    "text": "So...are you walking home with anyone after this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227000,
    "endTime": 228060,
    "duration": 1060,
    "text": "Just my friend Sayori."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232360,
    "endTime": 242420,
    "duration": 10060,
    "text": "JUST SAYORI!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242420,
    "endTime": 244660,
    "duration": 2240,
    "text": "J̴͖͓͊̐͝u̵̪̪͍̎͊s̴͓̆͠t̸̞̓ ̵̛͙̼͉̓̀M̶̯̳͍͒ǫ̷̖̾n̶̤͆̆ͅḯ̴̺͠k̵̦͚̄ͅa̵͓̔͌̀"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262440,
    "endTime": 264360,
    "duration": 1920,
    "text": "I know what you're thinking,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264360,
    "endTime": 269060,
    "duration": 4700,
    "text": "Oh no! Here he comes to tell us about VRV's $9.99 monthly subscription service."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269060,
    "endTime": 271100,
    "duration": 2040,
    "text": "He's gonna tease us with a free trial!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271100,
    "endTime": 274280,
    "duration": 3180,
    "text": "You think I'm gonna tempt you with the words 'ad free'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274280,
    "endTime": 277780,
    "duration": 3500,
    "text": "Or name drop a bunch of popular VRV programs like: Lastman, Harmon Quest,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277780,
    "endTime": 280860,
    "duration": 3080,
    "text": "and literally anything on Crunchyroll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280860,
    "endTime": 287420,
    "duration": 6560,
    "text": "You suspect I'm about to launch into an anecdotal spiel about downloading videos to your mobile device to watch later offline."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287420,
    "endTime": 292540,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "Kinda like I did with 5 seasons of RWBY, and 277 episodes of Fairy Tail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293240,
    "endTime": 297000,
    "duration": 3760,
    "text": "And you're almost certain I'm about flash the web address on screen (http://bit.ly/2c1cjmj)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297000,
    "endTime": 302380,
    "duration": 5380,
    "text": "And stare into your soul while you contemplate using the link below to sign up today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302380,
    "endTime": 305040,
    "duration": 2660,
    "text": "You think I'm reading from a teleprompter..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306560,
    "endTime": 307120,
    "duration": 560,
    "text": "I'm not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309320,
    "endTime": 310680,
    "duration": 1360,
    "text": "Thanks for watching"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310880,
    "endTime": 312560,
    "duration": 1680,
    "text": "I'm OR3O, I'm Adrisaurus"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312560,
    "endTime": 315420,
    "duration": 2860,
    "text": "And we both have music channels on YouTube"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315420,
    "endTime": 317660,
    "duration": 2240,
    "text": "You can check out more from our stuff on our channels."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317660,
    "endTime": 320920,
    "duration": 3260,
    "text": "And of course, you can always check out more Random Encounters videos right here on this channel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320940,
    "endTime": 323400,
    "duration": 2460,
    "text": "Beard salute OOOOHHHHHHH"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323920,
    "endTime": 325200,
    "duration": 1280,
    "text": "OOOOOHHHH"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325880,
    "endTime": 328480,
    "duration": 2600,
    "text": "Special thanks to our Patreon Encounters, like Javier Camarena."
  }
]